WEBVTT

07:27.933 --> 07:30.733
They have asked Me to speak in Hindi language.

07:30.973 --> 07:34.493
I think you people will excuse Me.

07:35.293 --> 07:40.293
Later on I'll explain to you what I said in short.

07:47.933 --> 07:51.813
Today we are standing at a point,

07:52.013 --> 07:56.373
which we can call as a dividing line

07:56.613 --> 07:59.973
between materialism and spirituality.

08:00.173 --> 08:05.173
I am going to speak on that subject in Hindi language.

08:05.413 --> 08:09.413
[HINDI ]

01:08:27.933 --> 01:08:34.213
I have told them only the pangs of materialism.

01:08:34.493 --> 01:08:39.333
How you people are suffering and how everything is sellable.

01:08:39.533 --> 01:08:42.573
Everything becomes sellable, chastity is sellable,

01:08:42.853 --> 01:08:45.333
goodness is sellable, everything is sellable.

01:08:45.533 --> 01:08:49.893
Then what happens, that you just have the money, so called,

01:08:50.093 --> 01:08:52.373
for a very short time,

01:08:52.613 --> 01:08:55.173
and actually people are bankrupt.

01:08:55.413 --> 01:08:58.573
Healthwise, mentally they are really bankrupt.

01:08:58.773 --> 01:09:03.413
So this materialism is to be understood in the Lakshmi principle,

01:09:03.613 --> 01:09:06.933
which is that you should have love.

01:09:07.173 --> 01:09:10.533
Lakshmi is the personification of love.

01:09:10.733 --> 01:09:16.173
She wears always a pink sari. Pink is the...

01:09:17.373 --> 01:09:22.893
... is the representative of her loving character.

01:09:23.093 --> 01:09:27.253
So if you can turn everything to love, materialism will be finished,

01:09:27.453 --> 01:09:29.653
because they are on opposite direction.

01:09:29.853 --> 01:09:32.293
And that's what I have tried to explain to them,

01:09:32.493 --> 01:09:37.733
by many references here and there, how you can overcome materialism.

01:09:38.053 --> 01:09:41.653
I wish somebody could translate this and give it to the people,

01:09:41.853 --> 01:09:43.693
so they can understand.

01:09:43.893 --> 01:09:46.533
But I think, with vibrations it will work out better.

01:09:46.733 --> 01:09:49.933
May God bless you.

01:09:50.173 --> 01:09:53.373
[ HINDI]
